Class BackgammonGame

  • java.lang.Object
    • BackgammonGame

  • public class BackgammonGame
extends java.lang.Object
    BackgammonGame orchestrator class which represents the main activities of a single backgammon game. Is used to update the scores of the players in the normal execution of a match
